                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         "Hair is crucial when trying to go from ugly or average, to a pretty woman. It common for a celebrity's or influencer's major hair transformation to determine their attractiveness. Many often wonder if they can pull off the new look. How can you take advantage of this? The first thing you must do is figuring out the shape of your face. Then go online and pick a look you want. Also, ask your trusted hairstylist for recommendations and spice things up. Mix it up and select the best look.",
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         "If you’re uncomfortable with makeup, that is completely alright. But if you want to transition from an ugly girl to pretty girl, a little make-up won’t harm you.If you’re someone who has sensitive skin, use only top quality, natural products. All you need as essentials in your make-up bag is some powder and a lip-gloss. It’ll immediately change the way you look and feel about yourself. Make-up is never a bad thing, well unless it’s overdone. If you’re someone who isn’t a big fan of well-done fancier make-up looks than just go for a much more natural one. It’ll only make you look and feel prettier than you already do. And these days you’ll find tons of YouTubers, influencers, bloggers, and even celebrities who do makeup tutorials where they also mention the products that they use and how one make-up product can be manipulated and used as another so you don’t have to carry the entire kit everywhere. But always make sure to get the right tones and shades of makeup that will suit your skin (Icy Tales).",
                                                                                                
                                                                                                                                "If you want to work on a budget and try taking baby steps into this whole transformation then start with what’s already there. If you’ve been blessed with a tiny waist, a great curvy figure, beautiful brown eyes, and long shiny hair, etc. Then try stepping out of the comfort zone. Wear belts around dresses to accentuate the waist, tighter dressed and peplums to show off that figure, take those glasses off so everyone can look into your beautiful eyes and let your long silky hair down instead of always typing it up. Start small, it’ll go a long way and make a big impact.  Trust me on this one, you won’t regret it. Do you have any idea how many women would kill to have features like yours? Find your strong suit, and work with it.",
                                                                    
                                                                                                                                              "If you want to go from being an ugly girl to pretty girl then you must always hold that head up high and be confident. This tip is to assure you that you don’t need chemicals, prosthetics, surgery, or extensions to look pretty. Well this is real life, and there is no fairy godmother in this fairytale of yours, but I’m here and I can help you so make sure that you read these tips carefully. One of the best tips that I can give you if you want to feel pretty and better about yourself is to be confident no matter what you do. Confidence is key! Think about it, when you’re attracted to someone or find somebody attractive and good looking, what do you think to yourself? That she’s bold and beautiful. So be brave, be bold, and then you’ll be beautiful. Believe in what you do. Walk confidently, work confidently, and present yourself confidently.",
                                                                                                                                              "One of the most important factors that you must pay attention is getting rid of junk food. Eating right is extremely important for your skin, your fitness, and your health. We all have our cravings so it’s okay to have a cheat meal every once in a while. But this one’s for you especially if you’re a student, working woman or a busy housewife who just doesn’t have the time to take care of herself and exercise either. This small change in your diet will go a long way. When you’re healthier, fitter, and have better clearer skin, you’ll automatically be more confident about your looks and your body. It can be very hard making these changes in your diet, nobody ever said it was easy. And as much as you love going home and having pizza, Chinese, or an extremely cheesy pasta every night, you must start to love yourself. And you do this by giving your body what it needs. Get rid of junk food and switch to healthy alternatives. But keep in mind that this does not mean you give up food altogether and stop eating. There are many ways to switch to a healthier lifestyle: some of them include meal prep, healthier alternatives, eating a lot but in short proportions and more constantly.",

                                                                            
                                                                                                                                              "Now we all know high heels are a huge pain, but let me tell you a little about all that wearing them will make you gain. Opting for high heels instead of those boring manly formal shoes or the same old flats that you wear every day is a sure way for you to transition from an ugly girl to pretty girl.  Wearing them will give you just that confidence boost that you needed. Also, it’ll help your figure look better, and your butt pop out. Men are always attracted to the sound of high heels clicking on floors. I’m sure you’ve experienced this before when you’re sitting at an airport, or a doctor’s office or maybe just a mall food court and then you hear the sound of high heels, and then you immediately turn your head to see who it is, and when you do you wonder to yourself, who is this glamorous pretty woman? Well here’s your chance to be that glamourous pretty woman. This is a great way to spice things up so you can feel like you’ve gone from an ugly girl to pretty girl.",
                                                                                            
                                                                                                                                              "Now, this is very important for someone who plans to turn from an ugly girl to pretty girl. If you want to look and feel pretty, you must have a pretty outfit to match that pretty face and pretty personality. It’s important that you keep up with the trends, and understand your body and what works for it. There are many how-to articles, videos, and even books both offline and online that you can use for reference if you aren’t sure about how to dress for your body type. This doesn’t mean that you must give up on your style entirely. Mix it up. Use silhouettes that work best on your body in colors and prints that are your style. But remember, they must also go along well with your skin tone. And your make-up, accessories, and footwear must all be in sync with the outfit. You shouldn’t seem to be dressed up as someone who did it all in the dark.",
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    "There are dozens of creams, face-washes, soaps, at home, and even clinical treatments for skincare. Use a face-mask every once in a while. Wash your face before going to bed every night. Moisturize. These are only some of the basics that you must follow to have good skin. You must also eat right for this. Having clear skin will make you feel so much better about yourself and love yourself even more. This is how you’ll feel great about yourself and pretty.",

                                                            "The last tip I have for you if you feel like you must go from an ‘ugly girl to pretty girl’ is to be yourself. Even though you are making all these physical changes to yourself and your lifestyle, don’t let that take away from your amazing personality. The best thing that could ever happen to anyone is when they feel comfortable and pretty in their skin. So, my number one tip to you if you want to feel pretty is that you start with loving yourself the way you are first and then move on to making these tweaks in your life."], with: ["https://media.istockphoto.com/id/1252858062/photo/beautiful-woman-wearing-stylish-sunglasses.jpg?s=612x612&w=0&k=20&c=Mn2QI1jobjZur6GCS19KNkencE72yMDPR560leEjWm4=", "https://media.istockphoto.com/id/1252858062/photo/beautiful-woman-wearing-stylish-sunglasses.jpg?s=612x612&w=0&k=20&c=Mn2QI1jobjZur6GCS19KNkencE72yMDPR560leEjWm4=", "https://media.istockphoto.com/id/1252858062/photo/beautiful-woman-wearing-stylish-sunglasses.jpg?s=612x612&w=0&k=20&c=Mn2QI1jobjZur6GCS19KNkencE72yMDPR560leEjWm4=", "https://media.istockphoto.com/id/1252858062/photo/beautiful-woman-wearing-stylish-sunglasses.jpg?s=612x612&w=0&k=20&c=Mn2QI1jobjZur6GCS19KNkencE72yMDPR560leEjWm4=", "https://media.istockphoto.com/id/1252858062/photo/beautiful-woman-wearing-stylish-sunglasses.jpg?s=612x612&w=0&k=20&c=Mn2QI1jobjZur6GCS19KNkencE72yMDPR560leEjWm4=", "https://media.istockphoto.com/id/1252858062/photo/beautiful-woman-wearing-stylish-sunglasses.jpg?s=612x612&w=0&k=20&c=Mn2QI1jobjZur6GCS19KNkencE72yMDPR560leEjWm4=", "https://media.istockphoto.com/id/1252858062/photo/beautiful-woman-wearing-stylish-sunglasses.jpg?s=612x612&w=0&k=20&c=Mn2QI1jobjZur6GCS19KNkencE72yMDPR560leEjWm4=", "https://media.istockphoto.com/id/1252858062/photo/beautiful-woman-wearing-stylish-sunglasses.jpg?s=612x612&w=0&k=20&c=Mn2QI1jobjZur6GCS19KNkencE72yMDPR560leEjWm4=", "https://media.istockphoto.com/id/1252858062/photo/beautiful-woman-wearing-stylish-sunglasses.jpg?s=612x612&w=0&k=20&c=Mn2QI1jobjZur6GCS19KNkencE72yMDPR560leEjWm4="])
                                                                                                                                                    
